            <title>[LUCENE-3676] Support SortedSource in MultiDocValues</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-3676</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;MultiDocValues doesn&apos;t support Sorted variant ie. SortedSource but throws UnsupportedOperationException. This forces users to work per segment. For consistency we should support sortedsource also if we wrap the DocValues in MDV.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
